data.description: Take a trip back to Olde Florida upon arrival at 10430 W Deep Creek Blvd. Mature trees canopy the long driveway leading up to the 3 Bedroom, 2 Bathroom house sitting on approximately 1.6 cleared & quiet acres.    Enjoy slow mornings on your screened in back porch overlooking the tranquil environment that surrounds the Deep Creek canal. The home sits far back from the road offering peace and privacy while still allowing ample backyard space for your family and furry friends to enjoy.   Don't miss out on this unique opportunity to own a piece of paradise in Hastings. Schedule your showing today!
